":769,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/10\/hearts-fingers-rahman\/","url_meta":{"origin":34644,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Qulub: Allah directs the hearts as He wills","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the hearts of the children of Adam, all of them, are between the two fingers of the Merciful as one heart. He directs them wherever He wills. O Allah, the Director of the hearts,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24961,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/allah-turns-heart-how-wills\/","url_meta":{"origin":34644,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hearts: O Allah, keep my heart steadfast upon Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would often say, \u201cO Turner of the hearts, keep my heart firm upon Your religion!\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2140 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0643\u0652\u062b\u0650\u0631\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19176,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/18\/tajdid-faith-hearts-shirt\/","url_meta":{"origin":34644,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Iman: Renew faith in your hearts before it wears out","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 18, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the faith of one of you will wear out within him, just as a shirt becomes worn out, so ask Allah to renew faith in your hearts.\" Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 14668 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/09\/prophet-anchors-muraqabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34644,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Istighfar: The Prophet anchors his mindfulness of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Aghar al-Muzani reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, there is fog over my heart at times, so I seek the forgiveness of Allah one hundred times in a day.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2702 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Muslim Al-Qadi said, \"It is said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u06